'''Amawal''' d adlis anida llan awalen n tutlayt neɣ taɣult n urmud, awalen ttmizwaren-d akken i-d-mmizwaren isekkilen [[Agemmay|ugemmay]], yal yiwen yid-s tabadut, asegzi d unamek ines.

llan aṭas imawalen di yal amḍiq n tussna, dɣa ad naf ula s teqbaylit neɣ s tmaziɣt s-umata, aṭas n imawalen i-d-yufraren, gar-asen:

''AMAWAL''  sɣuṛ ''[[Mulud Mɛemmri]]'' <br/>
''AMAWAL N TSENSELKIMT'' (Tafṛansist - Taglizit - Tamaziɣt) sɣuṛ ''Samiya Sɛad-Buzefran'' <ref>http://cedric.cnam.fr/~bouzefra/articles/Lexique_complet.pdf</ref><br/>
''ISSIN'', AMAWAL n teqbaylit s teqbaylit sɣur ''Kamal Buɛemara'' <ref>http://www.tamurt.info/avec-la-naissance-de-issin-on-peut,533.html</ref><br/>
''Iɣsan s teqbaylit'' sɣur ''Mohamed Zakaria BENRAMDANE''<ref>http://fr.scribd.com/doc/104359043/Ighsan-s-Teqbaylit-Vocabulaire-Kabyle-de-l%E2%80%99Osteologie-et-de-l%E2%80%99Orthopedie-par-Mohamed-Zakaria-BENRAMDANE</ref><br/>
''Amawal Lexique Des Sciences de La Terre'' sɣur ''Yidir ḤMED ZAYED''<ref>http://fr.scribd.com/doc/104357559/Amawal-Lexique-Des-Sciences-de-La-Terre-par-Yidir-AHMED-ZAYED</ref><br/>

